Package com.hannesdorfmann.mosby.mvp.delegate

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ActivityMvpDelegate<V extends MvpView,P extends MvpPresenter<V>>
    A delegate for Activities to attach them to mosbies mvp.
    FragmentMvpDelegate<V extends MvpView,P extends MvpPresenter<V>>
    A delegate for Fragments to attach them to mosby mvp.
    MvpDelegateCallback<V extends MvpView,P extends MvpPresenter<V>>
    The MvpDelegate callback that will be called from ActivityMvpDelegate or FragmentMvpDelegate or ViewGroupMvpDelegate.
    MvpViewStateDelegateCallback<V extends MvpView,P extends MvpPresenter<V>>
    An enhanced version of MvpDelegateCallback that adds ViewState support.
    MvpViewStateViewGroupDelegateCallback<V extends MvpView,P extends MvpPresenter<V>>
    An enhanced version of MvpViewStateDelegateCallback that adds ViewState support for android.view.View like FrameLayout etc.
    ViewGroupMvpDelegate<V extends MvpView,P extends MvpPresenter<V>>
    The mvp delegate used for everything that derives from View like FrameLayout etc.
